Clifford J. JUDD, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 11117. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. April 2, 1946. Joseph P. Lacey, Harmon D. Skillin, and Fred. McDonald, all of San Francisco, Cal., for appellant. Frank J. Hennessy, U. S. Atty., and Reynold H. Colvin, Asst. U. S. Atty., both of San Francisco, Cal., for appellee.

Before MATHEWS, IIEALY, and BONE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment of the District Court is affirmed.
